Description_lang: Gul'dan's keen eye allows him to cast $@spellname227551 when any additional target stands within $227551A1 yards of his primary target when attacking.$@spellname227551 cleaves at targets for $227550s1 Fire damage, divided amongst targets within $228163A1 yards, consuming all of Gul'dan's Fel Energy, increasing in damage by $227557s1% for every point of Fel Energy consumed.Each successful cast of $@spellname227551 grant's Gul'dan $@spellname227556.If Gul'dan ever reaches full Fel Energy, he immediately casts $@spellname227551 at his primary target.
